.Dd January 18, 2008
.Dt PCIB 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm pcib
.Nd PCI bridge driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
To compile this driver into the kernel,
place the following line in your
kernel configuration file:
.Bd -ragged -offset indent
.Cd "device pci"
.Ed
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides for host and
.Tn PCI
bridges in a
.Tn PCI
system.
